description: This Chainlink VRF common Plezier purrs with a rating of 51, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 102, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, 2 for East, Box for South, and 2 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70512-22424-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [102 Votes, Common]
